{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305973, "create_time": 1658374550, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "贾大山是一位“有着洞察社会人生的深邃目光和独特视角”的作家，他还提到其小说《取经》，并说“我曾读过几篇大山的小说，常常被他那诙谐幽默的语言、富有哲理的辨析、真实优美的描述和精巧独特的构思所折服”。\n见到麦家说：“我看过你的《暗算》《风声》，你是谍战剧第一人，歌颂的是爱国主义的精神，但是现在也有不少谍战影视剧不尊重历史，给观众造成了不良影响。”\n到贾平凹这里时问他“有没有新作？”贾平凹说，“我刚出版了一本叫《老生》的长篇小说。”", "timestamp": 1658374550}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305983, "create_time": 1658375136, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "东野圭吾《虚无的十字架》", "timestamp": 1658375136}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305986, "create_time": 1658375203, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "另外，“三观正”这种词还是少用，显得你自己容易被带偏。你只不过是想找些符合自己口味的东西，有什么资格评价别人是歪，你就是正？", "timestamp": 1658375203}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 305989, "create_time": 1658375257, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "而且，时刻带着审查思维，这个正，那个歪，不累吗？", "timestamp": 1658375257}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306011, "create_time": 1658375687, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re : 找点名著看吧", "timestamp": 1658375687}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306013, "create_time": 1658375754, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 虽然我也不喜欢三观正这个说法，不过起点某些热门的小说真的看了很麻啊", "timestamp": 1658375754}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 306018, "create_time": 1658376150, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Dave: 像我就不太喜欢以前的种马